QA polish: stronger OOP indicator and smarter pack-close routing

OOP cards now use a red glow halo + bold "OOP" badge at the bottom
of the card, replacing the subtle 2px outline that was hard to see
against the gold/silver/bronze fills. Cards also get a deeper
saturation drop so they read as visually penalized.

Reward packs from SBC and Season now route back to their source view
on close (e.g. "Back to SBCs" / "Back to Season") instead of always
dumping the user on the pack store. The "Open another" CTA is hidden
for reward packs (since they were a gift, not a purchase).

Threading: RFC.grantPack(packId, returnTo) and runOpening accepts
opts.returnTo. SBC submits and Season reward-claims pass their
view name so the close button reads correctly.
